			.detail.two-col
				p Leo and Oliver Kremer are genuinely, fiercely passionate about their Mexican food. Before them, I thought there wasn't a restaurant site in the world I'd want to do. Well I was wrong, because Dos Toros revolves around a true culture that isn't about selling burritos.
				p Their primary goal with the site was to tell their story and express the truly weird but passionate culture they have, they just had no idea how. That's where I came in, working closely with them and leading the design from first concepts to the full launched site.
