	.detail
		p Dos Toros started with two brothers who set out on a mission of passion, and I framed the homepage as 'A Tale of Two Brothers' to tell their story. It goes on to explain how they went about their mission...
		p The whole page heavily utilizes scrolling in some crazy ways. Some pretty awesome animation sequences happen completely based on scroll. With the help of M3's developers (who built the site,) I was able to work directly in the front-end in order to get the details of these animation sequences right, and balance the pacing of the story as I saw fit.
